data.description: Discover elegance in the revitalized 22nd Street with this remodeled 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home. Featuring a spacious living and formal dining area, this residence seamlessly combines comfort with modern sophistication. The highlight is a stunning kitchen with a large island, ideal for entertaining. The upper level hosts a luxurious owner's suite with a serene master bath, plus two additional bedrooms for privacy. This home also presents a  one-car garage and a fenced yard, enhancing outdoor space. A perfect blend of style and functionality, this home is a gem in a charming neighborhood.
